OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA generally
OL,6,Ffine evening and remaining dry for
OL,7,Fmost overnight with occasional clear
OL,8,Fintervals. Isolated showers are
OL,9,Fpossible, these most likely in the
OL,10,Fnorthwest where it will be windy at
OL,11,Ffirst.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FOften cloudy on Saturday
OL,14,Fwith showers possible, these mainly in
OL,15,Fthe north, where they could be heavy.
OL,16,FStaying dry for many though and
OL,17,Fpleasant when the sunshine appears.
OL,18,FLighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
