OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FAfter
OL,6,Fcold starts, Sunday and Monday will be
OL,7,Fdry with light winds and some
OL,8,Fsunshine. Freshening northeasterly
OL,9,Fwinds by Tuesday and feeling cooler
OL,10,Funderneath cloudier skies, with
OL,11,Fperhaps some showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
